title: Upgraded, cozy, quiet townhouse, lots of natural light
posting_body: ['Available NOW!', 'Bright, Beautiful, Two-story, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, townhouse for rent in Milpitas', 'High ceiling, large windows, and lots of natural light', 'One of the most quite houses in the complex with very good privacy', 'Quite and family neighborhood', 'Easy access to highways: 680, 237, and 880', 'Near shopping stores', 'Excellent Milpitas schools', '1550 sq ft living area', 'Garage: 2-car, attached', 'New paint, including garage', 'New carpet throughout the house', 'Newly remodeled bathrooms with granite vanity countertops', 'Granite counter-tops in kitchen', 'Appliances: new gas stove with oven, microhood, and dishwasher, refrigerator, washer, and dryer', 'Formal dinning room, formal living room', 'Wall-to-wall carpet, tile in the kitchen, newly upgraded tiles in all bathrooms', 'Central heating and cooling system', 'Energy efficient (LED) lights throughout', 'Gas fireplace with upgraded stone surround', 'Dual pane windows', 'Private front patio', 'Pool, spa, and large grill for parties, kids playground', 'Professionally landscaped grounds with cement walkways', 'Short walking distance to Dixon Landing park (baseball, cricket, basketball, and tennis courts)', 'Available to move', 'No animals and pets/No drugs/No smoking/No sublease', 'Good credit records required', 'References required', 'Viewing by appointment only, please text/call', 'show contact info', 'Rent: $4,000', 'Security Deposits: $4,500', 'Application Fee: $35.00', 'California Landing Villas, South of Dixon Landing park', '45 to Tracy, 25 min to Livermore, 25 min to Dublin / Pleasanton, 15 min to Fremont / Union City / Castro Valley / Hayward / San Ramon / Danville, 15 min to Newark / San Leandro / Foster City, 20 min to San Jose / Santa Clara / Sunnyvale, 20 min to Menlo Park / Palo Alto / Oakland / Alameda, 15 min to Mountain View / Cupertino / Redwood City /San', 'Mateo, 50 min to Berkeley, 50 min to San Francisco ).']
